! Photon-Chased Ferrite Trace Formation

Guided activation-front fabrication where light biases redox or mineral
deposition along a confined channel to form anisotropic ferrite-like traces.

!! Why It Matters

It gives the materials lane a controllable route from bio-templating or
chemistry into embedded magnetic/electrical trace geometry.

